
   Triclops Invasion 1.6 :              --- Public Domain ---

   CLI Options:     Triclops [Options]

      44            Use four bit planes.
      55            Use five bit planes.

      ))filename    RECORD MODE        Write a new demo file.
                    To enter a banner while recording,   just
                    start typing the banner, the game freezes
                    until a mouse button is pressed.  You can
                    cleanup or change the  banners  later  by
                    editing the demo file.

      ((filename    REPLAY MODE           Replay a demo file.
      rr            REPEAT        Repeat replay demo forever.
                    In replay modes,  clicking a mouse button
                    drops you out of the demo and  you  start
                    playing the game at that point.

   Examples:
      Triclops 44                         Play the game

      Triclops ))ram:mydemo 44            Play and record.

      edit       ram:mydemo               Fix up the banners

      Triclops ((ram:mydemo 55 rr         Replay continuously

   Startup:
      The game is slightly faster with only four bit  planes.
      Before the last globe of the  world  map  is  generated
      on the screen,  simply place the crosshair pointer over
      the spot on the world you wish the city to  be  placed.
      The selection of one of the  eight geodesic  satellites
      is controlled by the  x location  of  the  city  on the
      world map. Eight equal strips zones down the world map.
